        <ontology:hasDescription>The size of the area (km2) is 6317.996. The minimum altimetry of the LAU (Local Administrative Unit) is -3. The maximum altimetry of the LAU is 1307. The total population (in thousand) is 261.21. The population density (Inhabitants/km2) in the LAU is 41.34. The population change rate of the LAU in the last 10 years (%) has been 4.90%. The overall regional population density (Inhabitants/km2) is 75.32. The regional population change rate in the last 10 years (%) has been 5.12%.  </ontology:hasDescription>
